title: Person With White Cane Medium Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Visually Impaired Person Medium Skin Tone
description: A person with a white cane, representing blindness or low vision. The medium skin tone indicates a specific skin color.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the person with a white cane emoji presents a stylized figure with medium skin tone, confidently holding a white cane. Apple's design emphasizes smooth gradients and soft rounded edges, giving the figure a gentle yet resilient presence. The cane itself is depicted with a subtle sheen, reflecting the realistic lighting that gives it depth and form, symbolizing independence, awareness, and accessibility in digital conversations.
